<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BAWIPA NA THLUACHUAHNAK</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa na thluachuahnak, kan hmuhmi hi
 Rel cawk ding a, si lo, a liam in liam
 Thil zeizong hi kan ca, tuahmi an si
 Kan rel khawh tawk thluachuah, nak na kan pek.

[C1]
   Mifim mithiam zei hngal, lo te zong hi
   An mah le tawk cio in, fimnak na pek
   Inn le lo zeizong te, kan hmuh mi hi
   Bawipa sinin kan hmuh, mi lawng an si.

[V2]
 thingkung ramhnah, Pangpar, kan hmuhmi hi
 Sersiamtu cung, Pathian, sermi an si
 Tisik anhnah, eiding, kan hmuhmi hi
 Bawipa sin in kan hmuh, mi lawng an si.

[V3]
 Fa le ca i, thil tha, Ui lo tu cu
 Thil vialte nak in tha, Jesuh a kan pek
 Kan tuah kan tuan mi hi, Bawipa lo cun
 Thei a tlaiter kho tu, ho hmanh um lo.</lyrics>
<key>E</key>
</song>